IMAPStore bartol-remote
Host imap.fastmail.com
Port  993
User b@bartol.dev
PassCmd "gpg --batch -q --decrypt ~/.mutt/password.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

MaildirStore bartol-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/
Inbox ~/.mail/INBOX

Channel bartol
Master :bartol-remote:
Slave :bartol-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *
ExpireUnread no
